{"tid":1642800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再唔戴口罩反抗，就係默許左蒙面惡法","createTime":"2019-10-10T00:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:34:56.000Z","uid":315076,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f08db6174c3015aa00e09101fda374af68dc20ea","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"至從出左蒙面惡法<br />\n法院唔出臨時禁制令<br />\n當日見到個個都戴口罩出黎反抗<br />\n<br />\n一個二個都話：<br />\n再唔戴既話以後就無得戴。<br />\n我真係好感動。<br />\n但係過左幾日之後呢？<br />\n<br />\n真係成真架喎句野<br />\n話唔戴就唔戴<br />\n<br />\n而家好多就算有黑衫既<br />\n擺明係手足既人上街撚狗<br />\n都唔戴口罩<br />\n係比立法之前少左好L多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做乜事丫大家<br />\n之前講緊同烏克蘭比較<br />\n同西方國家既蒙面法乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知點解烏克蘭可以成功？<br />\n因為佢哋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民戴口罩</span></span><br />\n等我講下<br />\n日日全民口罩日<br />\n有咩理由<br />\n<br />\n如果係<span style=\"color: red;\">惡法</span><br />\n點解要遵守？！<br />\n<br />\n點解會多左人比狗上街截查！？！<br />\n就因為有手足上街戴口罩<br />\n街坊的唔戴<br />\n咁手足咪容易比人spot到囉！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要夠多人<br />\n成條街既人都戴口罩<br />\n班魔警先唔會咁易入手<br />\n無咁易無啦啦就拉人<br />\n無咁易無啦啦就拘捕<br />\n<br />\n只有<span style=\"color: red;\">全民戴口罩</span><br />\n先可以好好咁保護我地既手足<br />\n將手足融入於民眾當中！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家，<br />\n抗爭係要日常化<br />\n已經唔係叫你每晚大聲叫口號<br />\n而係選擇用<br />\n靜默，<br />\n不影響人，<br />\n和平方式，<br />\n保護自己健康<br />\n的方法<br />\n表達意見<br />\n<br />\n可能有人怕：<br />\n仆街<br />\n我戴口罩會比人捉<br />\n<br />\n但我想講<br />\n人人都做既時候<br />\n就會顯得安全<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"12d3f5c7ec4c9c42ac89b7dd372d0f817f1432b0","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0cb77712f05490e0a00b7a5a4028a65e631a5d8","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:58:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0c3cafa286722740e6256b2cb032eca5ef26d6c","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"532c0a3ccabc5aaeb39e216f5de4edb68ef5263f","tid":1642800,"uid":227139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"全民同我帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b065904c0fe0786c1b4a97e4fc0def09503656e","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:00:39.000Z","msg":"推到全民戴口罩！！！"},{"pid":"49c930c0ea176beb5fd63cfc22a5a2086722bc7c","tid":1642800,"uid":160996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"琴日下午行出銅鑼灣一轉<br />\n100個人先得3、4個人有戴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人，連咁和理非嘅行動都唔敢做<br />\n講乜嘢反抗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「香港人，反抗！」唔係得個嗌字</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e19f9eb54220f4a5491e1d12b46aae2cc02c4bd","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"推到全民戴口罩！！！"},{"pid":"4a98e7488068a0b400e15d2cb5c32681385ab7ab","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:02:41.000Z","msg":"推到全民戴口罩！！！"},{"pid":"afa161bfc7fa891eadda1c2752bd62790b969b71","tid":1642800,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c3d96ae92074b1c41a863129617da4de787e42","tid":1642800,"uid":315076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"推到全民戴口罩！！！"},{"pid":"70ce3cbf83ec095d58ddf119acb53216f7d7bf39","tid":1642800,"uid":307